8 December 2013Members of the media are reminded about the briefing to be held by Minister in The Presidency, Collins Chabane on developments relating to the state funeral of President Nelson Mandela. Minister Chabane will be joined by the Minister of DIRCO, Ms Maite Nkoana-Mashabane, the Minister of Transport, Ms Dipuo Peters, the City of Joburg Mayor, Mr Parks Tau and the Mandela Family. The details are as follows: Date: Sunday, 8 December 2013 Time: 15h00 Venue: SABC Studios, AucklandEnquiries: Phumla Williams Cell: 083 5010 139Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)